org.linqs.psl.model.predicate.model

Class ModelPredicate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.model.predicate.Predicate
      • org.linqs.psl.model.predicate.StandardPredicate
        • org.linqs.psl.model.predicate.model.ModelPredicate

  • public class ModelPredicate
extends StandardPredicate
    A predicate that is backed by some supporting model. Before a ModelPredicate can be used, loadModel() must be called.
